{
  "clauseRiskSummary": "This clause establishes joint and several liability for the Venture's harm, potentially exposing the non-operator to significant financial risk if a party's actions or inaction lead to losses.",
  "operative_text": "If the Venture is harmed as the result of an individual Member's action or failure to act, then that individual Member will be liable for that harm. If more than one Member is at fault then they will be jointly and severally liable for that harm.",
  "concerns": [
